verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Come, Christians, join to sing Alleluia! Amen!
Loud praise to Christ our King; Alleluia! Amen!
Let all, with heart and voice, before His throne
rejoice;
Praise is His gracious choice; Alleluia! Amen!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Come, lift your hearts on high, Alleluia! Amen!
Let praises fill the sky; Alleluia! Amen!
He is our Guide and Friend; to us He’ll
condescend;
His love shall never end; Alleluia! Amen!{/lang-eng}
